    "attributes": {
        "action": "Change the law so the driver not the owner is responsible for a PCN",
        "additional_details": "On a non endorseable ticket it\u2019s the owner not the driver that is liable \r\nHowever if you drive a company car your employer will more than likely pay the fine as ultimately they Will just deduct the money from this from your wages",
        "background": "My local council wrongly ticketed my company vehicle \r\nMy company paid this fine and because the fine was paid the council closed the matter making impossible to appeal the ticket \r\nBut my company then took this money from my wages leaving me out of pocket",
